P.S.
The xtexcad version 1.3 package is the final version of 
this software because nowadays, it is more convenient 
to import encapsulated PostScript graphics into a document. 
However, for little diagrams and graphics it still is
a very useful tool which furthermore produces portable
(i.e. non-binary) images.